Description:
In Call of Juarez: Gunslinger is all that should be in the story of the Wild West - from gold mines to dirty saloons. Go in the footsteps of the most dangerous criminals in the role of a desperate bounty hunter. Cross the boundary beyond which a person becomes a legend, and find out the truth about those whose names are immortalized in countless stories about the Wild West.
